Package net.canarymod.commandsys

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CommandListener
    Listener interface to mark a class a command class.
    CommandOwner
    This interface mandates methods for command ownership.
    NativeCommand
    Marks a command as a Canary native one
    PlayerSelector
    A class that handles the "@" attribute
    TabCompleteDispatch
    TabComplete method wrapper
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CanaryCommand
    Contains methods common to all types of chat commands.
    CommandList
    Canary "native" commands
    CommandManager
    Manages all commands.
    DynamicCommandAnnotation
    A fake Command annotation, used by the non-java based command system
    DynamicTabCompleteAnnotation
    A dynamic TabComplete annotation, used by the non-java based command system
    TabCompleteHelper
    A set of methods to help with doing tab completes
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CanaryCommandPermissions
    An list of all Canary Command permissions
    to help track what permissions are what
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CommandDependencyException
    Thrown when a commands parent command is not registered upon attempting to register the child command
    CommandException
    General catch-all class for exceptions that occur in commands.
    DuplicateCommandException
    Used to yell at a plugin developer for not checking their commands.
    TabCompleteException
    Exception thrown if a TabComplete method fails
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Command
    Used to annotate CommandListener methods and describe how a command should be handled within the CommandManager CanaryCommand
    TabComplete
    Annotation intended to help distinguish what methods are autoComplete methods in a CommandListener
